 2830: /**
 2831:  * Package filepath implements utility routines for manipulating filename paths
 2832:  * in a way compatible with the target operating system-defined file paths.
 2833:  * 
 2834:  * The filepath package uses either forward slashes or backslashes,
 2835:  * depending on the operating system. To process paths such as URLs
 2836:  * that always use forward slashes regardless of the operating
 2837:  * system, see the [path] package.
 2838:  */
