 2911:    * occurrences of "/" with `\`.
 2912:    * For example, Clean("//host/share/../x") returns `\\host\share\x`.
 2913:    * 
 2914:    * See also Rob Pike, “Lexical File Names in Plan 9 or
 2915:    * Getting Dot-Dot Right,”
 2916:    * https://9p.io/sys/doc/lexnames.html
 2917:    */
