15116:  * approximately 20 milliseconds, even if the wall clock is changed during
15117:  * the operation being timed:
15118:  * 
15119:  * ```
15120:  * 	start := time.Now()
15121:  * 	... operation that takes 20 milliseconds ...
15122:  * 	t := time.Now()
15123:  * 	elapsed := t.Sub(start)
